title: MichaelPro MP018006 6-Inch Deep Coping Saw, Coping Frame comes with Replacement Blades, Hand Woodworking Tool
features: 【HEAVY DUTY FRAME】Specially crafted with durability in mind, our deep coping saws are made of heavy duty frames that allows for longer life span and you do not have to worry about our saws breaking on the job.
